## 📋 Command Usage

```bash
# Interactive (asks questions)
@orchestrate

# Quick spawn (1 stream + N forks for current context)
@orchestrate --quick=3

# Specify a PRD to implement in parallel
@orchestrate --prd=payment-integration --forks=3

# Full orchestration setup
@orchestrate --streams=2 --forks=2 --prd-file=docs/prds/SWARM-PLAN.md

# Explicit backend
