```

### Parameters

| Parameter | Values | Default | Description |
|-----------|--------|---------|-------------|
| `--quick` | 1-8 | - | Quick spawn N forks (1 stream, current context) |
| `--streams` | 1-8 | 1 | Number of streams (tabs in iTerm2) |
| `--forks` | 1-8 | 2 | Number of forks per stream (panes in iTerm2) |
