## 🔗 Message Protocol

Communication with streams uses this message format:

```typescript
interface AgentMessage {
  from: string;           // "orchestrator" | "stream-a" | etc
  to: string;             // Target agent
  type: MessageType;      // Event type
  payload: Record<string, any>;
  timestamp?: string;     // Auto-added
}

type MessageType = 
  | 'register'           // Stream registering with orchestrator
  | 'prd_assignment'     // Orchestrator assigning PRD to stream
  | 'story_complete'     // Stream reporting story completion
  | 'prd_complete'       // Stream reporting PRD completion
  | 'continue'           // Orchestrator telling stream to proceed
  | 'revision_needed'    // Orchestrator requesting fixes
  | 'blocked'            // Stream reporting blocked status
  | 'error'              // Error report
  | 'status_update';     // General status update
```

